item.title: About me
item.author: thanhcong.le1108@gmail.com (Lê Thành Công)
item.description: My name is Lê Thành Công. This blog was created when i was a fresher Zalo Pay at VNG 2019. I’m also a student on the third year at Ho Chi Minh University of Science. I think this is a turning point that will change my mindset and determine my career in the future… “Keep moving forward. One step at a time.”
